<h2 id=3D"creating-path-specific-custom-instructions" tabindex=3D"-1"><a cl=
ass=3D"heading-link" href=3D"https://docs.github.com/en/copilot/how-tos/con=
figure-custom-instructions/add-repository-instructions#creating-path-specif=
ic-custom-instructions">Creating path-specific custom instructions<span cla=
ss=3D"heading-link-symbol" aria-hidden=3D"true"></span></a></h2>
<div class=3D"ghd-alert ghd-alert-accent" data-container=3D"alert"><p class=
=3D"ghd-alert-title"><svg version=3D"1.1" width=3D"16" height=3D"16" viewBo=
