s-for-repository-custom-instructions-4">Prerequisites for repository custom=
 instructions<span class=3D"heading-link-symbol" aria-hidden=3D"true"></spa=
n></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p>You must have a custom instructions file (see the instructions below).</=
p>
</li>
<li>
<p>The latest version of the Copilot extension must be installed in Xcode.<=
/p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"creating-custom-instructions-4" tabindex=3D"-1"><a class=3D"headi=
